#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:105
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Ssstranger, Ssstranger! Now thisss isss a ssstrange place to find each "
"other in, eh? Thossse cube people ssseem sssurprisssingly friendly asss "
"well. I actually came here to help you out in your missssion; can't let my "
"mossst valuable cussstomer die on me, can I? Although, I'm afraid we might "
"only have a sssingle ssshot at leaving thisss place, ssso how about I join "
"your crew for the time being? After we do our ussssual trading of "
"courssse.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:107
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_sylvan\"]/text"
msgstr "(Sylvan) Use Sylvan to hail Sylvan."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:109
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_sylvan\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"I ssssee you are not the ssstranger but rather me, me. I'm afraid no "
"dissscountsss though. There's an infinite me'sss and I can't go giving all "
"of them free ssscrap! Heheh... heh... You sssshould know thisss.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:112
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_sylvan\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:120
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_guntput\"]/text"
msgstr "(Guntput) Guntput wishes to speak to Sylvan."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:122
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_guntput\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"When Sylvan sees Guntput, he gulps but stays silent. Guntput frowns, "
"\"Stupid Slug man! You hide in big ship but send Renegade to help us? Where "
"were you when Anurak murdered, or when Hektar returns? Nowhere, as I saw! "
"Some hero you are, you are coward! Greedy corrupt Slug like all the others, "
"and with less excuse too!\" Guntput spits, just for good measure."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:124
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_guntput\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:126
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_guntput\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You expect Sylvan to retort, but instead he just chuckles uncomfortably. "
"\"Well Guntput, I'm glad you're alive at leasssst. Heh...\" Sylvan falls "
"silent for a moment. \"Well, would you ssstill care to trade sssstranger? "
"Thossse goodsss won't sssell themsssselvesss you know.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:128
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_guntput\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:138
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "See what he's offering."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:142
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "Sell some resources first."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:147
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_loc_cylvan_quest\"]/text"
msgstr "Sylvan has a story he wants to tell."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:152
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice[6]/text"
msgstr "Attack!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:156
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice[7]/text"
msgstr "Decline his offer."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:158
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice[7]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Maybe a different time then, ssstranger! I'm certain thisss won't be the "
"lassst we sssee each other, in thisss reality or another.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:160
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice[7]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:164
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH\"]/choice[7]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:172
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_CYLVAN_STORY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Ssstranger! While I made myssself acquainted with thisss sssector I came acrossss sssomething very unexpected: another Sssylvan already made thisss place their home! Not only that, it ssseemsss that they befriended the Obelisssksss living here, to the point they gave him hisss own unique cruissser!\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\"Now, He told me that he wasss being tracked by sssome very powerful Autosss. He refusssed to tell me why they were after him, but whatever the reassson, I sssussspect our interference with thisss sssector might have caussse whoever sssent thossse Autosss to want to take advantage of the commotion. We ssshould go check up on him once we are done trading.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:177
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_CYLVAN_STORY\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Sure."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:179
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_CYLVAN_STORY\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "\"Thank you, Ssstranger, now, care for some trading?\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:184
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_CYLVAN_STORY\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:192
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_CYLVAN_STORY\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Decline."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:194
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_CYLVAN_STORY\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"That'ssss alright, ssstranger. At leassst you ssseem confident in your "
"ssship!\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:196
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_CYLVAN_STORY\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:206
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_TRADE_COMMONWEALTH\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Aaaaah. Ssstranger ssstranger, before I found myself stuck in this "
"ssstrange place I made sssure to ssstock up on all the valuable aether "
"weaponsss I could find. Take a look!\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:207
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_TRADE_COMMONWEALTH\"]/crewMember"
msgstr "Sylvan"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:212
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH_ATTACK\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"For some insane reason, you have decided to attack the traveling merchant. "
"Are you REALLY sure you want to do this? This might be the strongest enemy "
"you'll ever face, so you better be prepared if you're going to take him on."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:214
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH_ATTACK\"]/choice[@req=\"challenge_level\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "Yes!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:216
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH_ATTACK\"]/choice[@req=\"challenge_level\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You raise your weapons against Sylvan, ready to battle. \"Ssstranger, ssso "
"it'sss come to thisss? A true ssshame... and to think I thought we could be "
"friendsss...\""

