"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH_CONVERT_FUEL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Fuel! Heh heh, can never have enough. But I'll take sssome off of your "
