#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:706
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH_CYLVAN\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "This is the location of a quest from the Traveling Merchant."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:707
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH_CYLVAN\"]/beaconType/visitedTooltip"
msgstr "Explored location. Nothing left of interest."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:709
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH_CYLVAN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You've arrived at the coordinates Sylvan gave. In the distance you can see a"
" two ships in the middle of an intense dogfight. You see both the Obelisk "
"ship your Sylvan talked about as well as a strange Auto-ship that seems "
"heavily well armed."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:712
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH_CYLVAN\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Attack the Auto!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:714
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH_CYLVAN\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You aim carefully and hit auto's piloting engines, disabling it for the "
"fight!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:718
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH_CYLVAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:724
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH_CYLVAN\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Attack Sylvan!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:726
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH_CYLVAN\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Commonwealth Sylvan is caught off guard by your first try, you manage to"
" hit their engines and force them to run at half power for the fight."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:735
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH_CYLVAN\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:741
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH_CYLVAN\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "We can't be the only ones looking for this. Leave."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:743
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH_CYLVAN\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You might never see that tech that Sylvan promised, but it's better than "
"being dead."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:745
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH_CYLVAN\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:749
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH_CYLVAN\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:757
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_CYLVAN_RUN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"You think you can jussst run away after what you have done?! Nonono! You "
"will finisssh this!\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:774
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH_CYLVAN_PROBE_FRIEND\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Sylvan is overjoyed to see you, \"Ssstranger! It makes me so happy to see that the ally of my people was the one to save me! That probe was much tougher than I expected, when I saw it attacking one of my people I...I couldn't just sit there and watch, you know?\" \n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\"But that's in the past, right ssstranger? I suppose I can't hide here forever, I know you want to escape this place, so let me join your crew, it's the least I can do. While you are at it, you might as well have the blueprints for my ship, it served me well and so it will serve you well as well.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:777
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH_CYLVAN_PROBE_FRIEND\"]/crewMember"
msgstr "Cylvan"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:782
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH_CYLVAN_PROBE_FRIEND\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:788
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH_CYLVAN_PROBE_NEUTRAL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Sylvan is relieved to see you, \"Ssstranger! Thank you for putting your life on the line to save me! That probe was much tougher than I expected, when I saw it attacking one of my people I...I couldn't just sit there and watch, you know?\" \n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\"But that's in the past, right ssstranger? I suppose you might as well have the blueprints for my ship, you earned it after all.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:795
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH_CYLVAN_PROBE_NEUTRAL\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:801
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH_CYLVAN_PROBE_ENEMY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Strangely Sylvan doesn't say anything, instead he beams what seems to be the"
" blueprints for his ship and a present. Your sensors can detect it's a bomb "
"and so you nearly avoid a disaster. It makes sense, he must not be happy "
"about all the Commonwealths you killed."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:805
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH_CYLVAN_PROBE_ENEMY\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:811
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH_CYLVAN_DEFEAT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Cylvan's hull finally breaks apart; even aether hulls can't take punishment forever, as you know well by now. Strangely, you are hailed by the Auto-ship you were sent here to kill. It's badly damaged enough that its ship recognition systems seem to be completely broken, as it thinks you are another member of whatever faction it belongs to. \n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\"Continuity has been enforced thanks to: you. Please accept this as a reward and return this package back to Prime.\" The auto ship transfers over a strange and powerful weapon as well as the blueprints to a cruiser sized auto ship!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:822
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_COMMONWEALTH_CYLVAN_DEFEAT\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:837
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"NEMESIS\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/text"
msgstr "(Leah) \"You aren't the beam master, I am!\"."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:839
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"NEMESIS\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The other Leah's eyes widen before she narrows them, a grin spreading across"
" her face. \"So it's true! The Federation managed to convince some other me "
"to join them. I have no clue how you managed to do that, beyatch, but this "
"universe isn't big enough for two Leahs. Get ready to be beamed, beyatch!\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:841
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"NEMESIS\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Here we go again."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:854
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"SYLVAN_ROYAL_NORMAL\"]/mod:findLike/mod:findLike/mod:findLike/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:choice/text"
msgstr "Ah, I remember. You must be Leah!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:856
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"SYLVAN_ROYAL_NORMAL\"]/mod:findLike/mod:findLike/mod:findLike/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Wait... you remembered?! Of... of course you did! I wouldn't expect "
"anything less from my nemesis! It's time to settle the score once and for "
"all, beyatch!\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:858
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"SYLVAN_ROYAL_NORMAL\"]/mod:findLike/mod:findLike/mod:findLike/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Let's finish this."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:860
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"SYLVAN_ROYAL_NORMAL\"]/mod:findLike/mod:findLike/mod:findLike/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You stare down your nemesis, both of you readying every weapon you have!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:863
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"SYLVAN_ROYAL_NORMAL\"]/mod:findLike/mod:findLike/mod:findLike/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:869
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"SYLVAN_ROYAL_NORMAL\"]/mod:findLike/mod:findLike/mod:findLike/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_jerry\"]/text"
msgstr "(Jerry) Wait... is there no other way to end this?"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:884
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"SYLVAN_ROYAL_DEAD\"]/mod:findLike/mod:findLike/mod-"
"append:choice/text"
msgstr "Ah, I remember. You must be Leah!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:886
