"append:choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_jerry\"]/text"
msgstr "(Jerry) Wait... is there no other way to end this?"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:909
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_LEAH_JERRY_ROYAL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Leah is taken aback at the sight of Jerry aboard your ship. \"Jerry?! What are you doing here?! There's no way Vance would ever let you be somewhere so dangerous!\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\tJerry sighed. \"It's... a long, long story. Look, Leah. This whole operation my uncle's doing is... a giant mistake. There's no way this will end well. I know how persistent you can be - such determination shouldn't be thrown away on some terrible, doomed plan! What if... you joined us instead?\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:913
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_LEAH_JERRY_ROYAL\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:915
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_LEAH_JERRY_ROYAL\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Leah just blinks, baffled by Jerry's offer. \"You... y-you're really asking me to join my arch-nemesis? Jerry... ugh, look. I like you, but this is a really, really tough ask. How do I know this isn't a trap?\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\"Come on, Leah! Why would your best friend lie to you?\" Jerry covertly winks to you as Leah takes a step back. \"You... you think we're... best friends...? In that case... fiiiiine. But you better give me the best room in the whole ship, beyatch!\" Jerry sighs with relief as Leah teleports over."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:918
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_LEAH_JERRY_ROYAL\"]/choice/event/crewMember"
msgstr "Leah"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:920
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_LEAH_JERRY_ROYAL\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Wait! What about Sylvan?"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:928
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_LEAH_JERRY_ROYAL_DEAD\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Leah is taken aback at the sight of Jerry aboard your ship. \"Jerry?! What are you doing here?! There's no way Vance would ever let you be somewhere so dangerous!\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\tJerry sighed. \"It's... a long, long story. Look, Leah. This whole operation my uncle's doing is... a giant mistake. There's no way this will end well. I know how persistent you can be - such determination shouldn't be thrown away on some terrible, doomed plan! What if... you joined us instead?\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:932
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_LEAH_JERRY_ROYAL_DEAD\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:934
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_LEAH_JERRY_ROYAL_DEAD\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Leah just blinks, baffled by Jerry's offer. \"You... y-you're really asking me to join my arch-nemesis? Jerry... ugh, look. I like you, but this is a really, really tough ask. How do I know this isn't a trap?\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\"Come on, Leah! Why would your best friend lie to you?\" Jerry covertly winks to you as Leah takes a step back. \"You... you think we're... best friends...? In that case... fiiiiine. But you better give me the best room in the whole ship, beyatch!\" Jerry sighs with relief as Leah teleports over."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:937
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_LEAH_JERRY_ROYAL_DEAD\"]/choice/event/crewMember"
msgstr "Leah"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:943
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Oh, right! That little Slug boy put up quite the fight, although I'm not "
"sure why he'd shut off his shields for the fight.\" You glare at Leah, "
"unsure what to say about her comment, before turning to Sylvan's chest."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:948
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Inspect the merchant's ship."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:950
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems Sylvan is in horrible condition. Leah might have been stronger than"
" before, but there's no way she single handedly killed him. Sylvan must have"
" already been worn down by the fleet of Obelisks and Aces to get here. You "
"aren't sure if you can save him."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:952
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "There's nothing we can do."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:954
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You know you can't save him, but you can at least make the merchant's final "
"moments comfortable. \"Ssstranger, thisss isss the end. I want you... to "
"have thissss... You're the Multiverssse'ssss biggessst badassss now. Go make"
" me proud.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:959
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_obyn\"]/text"
msgstr "(Obyn) \"My dearest Sylvan!\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:961
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_obyn\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"You weren't wrong Obyn... we did ssssee each other again...\" Sylvan puts "
"his hand to his chest, as if feeling if he still has a pulse. His face shows"
" a look of disappointment at what he feels. \"I don't have much longer, "
"Obyn. Do you remember that sssship we sssaid we would build together? "
"Well... I finissshed it. The blueprintsss in my cargo bay. If there'ssss one"
" thing I can trussst about my ssship, it'sss that the cargo bay alwaysss "
"sssurvivesss the fight...\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:963
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_obyn\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:965
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_obyn\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Thank you sssstranger, for reuniting me with Obyn one lassst time. It "
"hasss been an honor. There'sss a little extra sssomething in that cargo bay "
"for you.\" Sylvan turns to Obyn one last time. \"Obyn... I love you. "
"Goodbye.\" And with that, the traveling merchant slumps over unconscious. "
"Obyn's tears mark stains on his robes, and you aren't sure if you can do "
"anything to save him."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:968
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_obyn\"]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "There's nothing we can do. Go check the cargo bay."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:972
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_obyn\"]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"medbay\"]/text"
msgstr "(Adv. Medbay) Save him."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:974
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_obyn\"]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"medbay\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You rush Sylvan to the Medbay to be healed. Once he's in a stable condition,"
" he thanks you. Sylvan and Obyn have another one of their awkward distant "
"hugs, and then Sylvan turns to you. \"Well, ssstranger. Guessss we better "
"check on that cargo, then go sssave reality, eh?\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:975
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_obyn\"]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"medbay\"]/event/crewMember"
msgstr "Sylvan"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:977
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_obyn\"]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"medbay\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Go check the cargo bay."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:983
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_obyn\"]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"clonebay\"]/text"
msgstr "(Adv. Clone Bay) Save him."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:985
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_obyn\"]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"clonebay\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You rush to register Sylvan in your Clone Bay. Once his clone emerges from "
"it, he thanks you. Sylvan and Obyn have another one of their awkward distant"
" hugs, and then Sylvan turns to you. \"Well, ssstranger. Guessss we better "
"check on that cargo, then go sssave reality, eh?\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:986
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_obyn\"]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"clonebay\"]/event/crewMember"
msgstr "Sylvan"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:988
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_obyn\"]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"clonebay\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Go check the cargo bay."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:994
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_obyn\"]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"RECON_AND_TELEPORT\"]/text"
msgstr "(Reconstructive Teleporter) Save him."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:996
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_obyn\"]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"RECON_AND_TELEPORT\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You quickly beam back Sylvan and allow the regenerative effects of the "
"teleporter to kick in. Sylvan and Obyn have another one of their awkward "
"distant hugs, and then Sylvan turns to you. \"Well, ssstranger. Guessss we "
"better check on that cargo, then go sssave reality, eh?\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:997
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_obyn\"]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"RECON_AND_TELEPORT\"]/event/crewMember"
msgstr "Sylvan"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:999
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_obyn\"]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"RECON_AND_TELEPORT\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Go check the cargo bay."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1009
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_VARIANT_BILLY\"]/text"
msgstr "(Billy) Billy seems to want to say something."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1011
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_VARIANT_BILLY\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Billy rushes over to Sylvan, shaking him, trying to lift him off the floor. "
"\"Come on brother, don't die here! Oh, how could I let ussss grow ssso "
"apart, I'm ssssuch a fool. An assshole... Pleassse Sssylvan, don't let our "
"sssaga end here before I had a chance to redeem myssself.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1013
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_VARIANT_BILLY\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1015
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_VARIANT_BILLY\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Sylvan tries to sit up, but groans in pain. \"Even to the lassst minute, you"
" care more about yourssself. You drove me away from Hektar jussst ssso you "
"could keep up your little sssslave trade with that bassstard Irwin. And look"
" where that got both of you.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1017
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_VARIANT_BILLY\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1019
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_VARIANT_BILLY\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Billy starts sobbing uncontrollably. \"I know, I know. Pleasssse Sssylvan, I"
" can't watch you die. I don't want to lossse my brother, you're the only "
"perssson who ever wasss by my ssside.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1022
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_VARIANT_BILLY\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1024
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_VARIANT_BILLY\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Sylvan puts a tentacle on Billy's suit, pulling him closer. \"It'ssss far "
"too late to apologize for the passst. You want to make up for your passsst? "
"Accept you're a sssshit person, move forward, and help the sssstranger blow "
"thessse Rebelsss and cube freakssss to kingdom come.\" Sylvan slumps over, "
"unconscious. Billy begs for you to do something - anything."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1026
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_VARIANT_BILLY\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "There's nothing we can do."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1028
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_VARIANT_BILLY\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You know you can't save him, but you can at least make the merchant's final "
"moments comfortable. \"Ssstranger, thisss isss the end. I want you... to "
"have thissss... You're the Multiverssse'ssss biggessst badassss now. Go make"
" me proud.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1033
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_VARIANT_BILLY\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"medbay\"]/text"
msgstr "(Adv. Medbay) Save him."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1035
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_VARIANT_BILLY\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"medbay\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You rush Sylvan to the Medbay to be healed. Once he's in a stable condition,"
" he thanks you. Billy and Sylvan stare at each other awkwardly for a few "
"moments, until Sylvan finally says, \"Right now, we have more important "
"thingsss to do. Let'ssss go sssave reality, and talk about family drama "
"later.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1036
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_VARIANT_BILLY\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"medbay\"]/event/crewMember"
msgstr "Sylvan"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1041
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_VARIANT_BILLY\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"clonebay\"]/text"
msgstr "(Adv. Clone Bay) Save him."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1043
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_VARIANT_BILLY\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"clonebay\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You rush to register Sylvan in your Clone Bay. Once his clone emerges from "
"it, he thanks you. Billy and Sylvan stare at each other awkwardly for a few "
"moments, until Sylvan finally says, \"Right now, we have more important "
"thingsss to do. Let'ssss go sssave reality, and talk about family drama "
"later.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1044
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_VARIANT_BILLY\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"clonebay\"]/event/crewMember"
msgstr "Sylvan"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1049
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_VARIANT_BILLY\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"RECON_AND_TELEPORT\"]/text"
msgstr "(Reconstructive Teleporter) Save him."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1051
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_VARIANT_BILLY\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"RECON_AND_TELEPORT\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You quickly beam back Sylvan and allow the regenerative effects of the "
"teleporter to kick in. Billy and Sylvan stare at each other awkwardly for a "
"few moments, until Sylvan finally says, \"Right now, we have more important "
"thingsss to do. Let'ssss go sssave reality, and talk about family drama "
"later.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1052
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_VARIANT_BILLY\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"RECON_AND_TELEPORT\"]/event/crewMember"
msgstr "Sylvan"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1065
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"medbay\"]/text"
msgstr "(Adv. Medbay) Save him."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1067
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"medbay\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You rush Sylvan to the Medbay to be healed. Once he's in a stable condition,"
" he thanks you. \"Way to sssshow the Rebellion we don't messss around! "
"Ssstranger, you have done me a great ssservice. I shall now be at "
"yourssss.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1068
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"medbay\"]/event/crewMember"
msgstr "Sylvan"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1073
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"clonebay\"]/text"
msgstr "(Adv. Clone Bay) Save him."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1075
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"clonebay\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You rush to register Sylvan in your Clone Bay. Once his clone emerges from "
"it, he thanks you. \"Way to sssshow the Rebellion we don't messss around! "
"Ssstranger, you have done me a great ssservice. I shall now be at "
"yourssss.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1076
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"clonebay\"]/event/crewMember"
msgstr "Sylvan"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1081
