"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"RECON_AND_TELEPORT\"]/text"
msgstr "(Reconstructive Teleporter) Save him."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1083
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"RECON_AND_TELEPORT\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You quickly beam back Sylvan and allow the regenerative effects of the "
"teleporter to kick in. \"Way to sssshow the Rebellion we don't messss "
"around! Ssstranger, you have done me a great ssservice. I shall now be at "
"yourssss.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1084
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"RECON_AND_TELEPORT\"]/event/crewMember"
msgstr "Sylvan"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1154
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_MV_TRAVELER_BOSS_COMMONWEALTH_CRUISER_NORMAL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"From out of the tunnel comes a massive cruiser vessel, of a design you have "
"never seen before! This ship looks... ancient, yet millennia beyond yours in"
" terms of advancement. The captain hails you."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1158
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_MV_TRAVELER_BOSS_COMMONWEALTH_CRUISER_NORMAL\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1160
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_MV_TRAVELER_BOSS_COMMONWEALTH_CRUISER_NORMAL\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
