"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_MV_TRAVELER_BOSS_COMMONWEALTH_CRUISER_CHAOS\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"BRIBE_CHAOS\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You offer a tribute in desperation, but the Renegade doesn't display any "
"sort of reaction whatsoever. Instead it is the gnome that scoops up your "
"fuel, and the ship cuts contact with you. Better to not ask questions."

