"\"TRIBUTE DETECTED. HOSTILE SYSTEMS: POWERED DOWN. WARNING GIVEN.\" The auto"
" ship says before jumping away."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1524
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_MV_TRAVELER_BOSS_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN_EXTREME\"]/choice[@req=\"JUDGE_BOON_RENEGADE\"]/text"
msgstr "Use your blessing to avoid combat."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1530
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_MV_TRAVELER_BOSS_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN_CHAOS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"From out of the tunnel comes a massive cruiser vessel, of a design you have never seen before! This ship looks... ancient, yet millennia beyond yours in terms of advancement. It also seems to be mostly automated, however your sensors still detect crew inside it. The ship hails you:\n"
"\n"
"\t\"EXTERMINATOR DETECTED! THREAT COUNTERMEASURES INITIATED! COMBAT PROTOCOLS INITIATED.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1536
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_MV_TRAVELER_BOSS_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN_CHAOS\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Prepare to fight!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1538
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_MV_TRAVELER_BOSS_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN_CHAOS\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "\"PERISH TYRANT. FOR THE COMMONWEALTH'S FREEDOM.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1541
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_MV_TRAVELER_BOSS_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN_CHAOS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1547
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_MV_TRAVELER_BOSS_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN_CHAOS\"]/choice[@req=\"BRIBE_CHAOS\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "Pay the tribute to avoid the fight."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1558
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_MV_TRAVELER_BOSS_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN_CHAOS\"]/choice[@req=\"BRIBE_CHAOS\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "*%$##@*%!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1564
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_MTBOSS_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN_DESTROYED\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The mighty vessel has been eliminated! Within its wreckage remains plenty of"
" scrap and supplies for the taking."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1568
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_MTBOSS_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN_DESTROYED\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1575
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//eventList[@name=\"FR_MTBOSS_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN_DROP_CHANCE\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"You find the remains of a unique weapon model among the ruins of the ship, "
"but it appears it did not survive the fight. You'll have to be more careful "
"next time, or get lucky. Fortunately, there's still a bit more supplies to "
"take with you."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1582
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_MTBOSS_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN_DEADCREW\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The mighty vessel has been vanquished! Within the now cleared cruiser, "
"plenty of scrap and supplies remain for the taking."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1587
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_MTBOSS_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN_DEADCREW\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1593
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_MTBOSS_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN_DROP\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You're also surprised to find a special item among the wreckage! You've "
"never seen anything even remotely close to something like this before, so "
"you assume it's a custom drone, made by whatever strange species the "
"Renegades were."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1600
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_MTBOSS_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN_DESTROYED_CHAOS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The mighty vessel has been eliminated! Within its wreckage remains plenty of"
" scrap and supplies for the taking."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1604
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_MTBOSS_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN_DESTROYED_CHAOS\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1611
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//eventList[@name=\"FR_MTBOSS_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN_DROP_CHANCE_CHAOS\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"You find the remains of a unique weapon model among the ruins of the ship, "
"but it appears it did not survive the fight. You'll have to be more careful "
"next time, or get lucky. Fortunately, there's still a bit more supplies to "
"take with you."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1618
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_MTBOSS_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN_DEADCREW_CHAOS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The mighty vessel has been vanquished! Within the now cleared cruiser, "
"plenty of scrap and supplies remain for the taking."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1623
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_MTBOSS_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN_DEADCREW_CHAOS\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1629
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_MTBOSS_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN_DROP_CHAOS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You're also surprised to find a special item among the wreckage! You've "
"never seen anything even remotely close to something like this before, so "
"you assume it's a custom weapon, made by whatever strange species the "
"Renegades were."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1645
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ZOLTAN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Present your Salt crew."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1647
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ZOLTAN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"That... that's... a Salt person... one which isn't... that bounty "
"hunter... how...? I... I thought this was impossible... You can say I am... "
"flabbergasted. Well done, traveler. Expect... rewards before your next "
"journey.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1651
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ZOLTAN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1657
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ZOLTAN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Present a Totality Commander."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1659
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ZOLTAN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"The counterparts to the Rebellion's finest... What they lack in "
"firepower... they more than make up with sustainability and speed. Having "
"one in your crew is... most impressive. Well done, traveler. Expect... "
"rewards before your next journey.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1663
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ZOLTAN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1669
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ZOLTAN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Present your Spherax crew."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1671
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ZOLTAN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"That... that form... I was certain they had vanished before... and yet, "
"traveler... you have acquired this... unbelievable follower. I'm speechless."
" Well done, traveler. Expect... rewards before your next journey.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1675
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ZOLTAN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[3]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1681
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ZOLTAN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[4]/text"
msgstr "Present Obyn."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1683
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ZOLTAN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Ah... the great... bounty hunter... the last one of his kind... such a "
"heavy weight placed... on his shoulders. Well done, traveler. Expect... "
"rewards before your next journey.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1687
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ZOLTAN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[4]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1693
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ZOLTAN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[5]/text"
msgstr "Present your Commonwealth crew."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1695
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ZOLTAN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[5]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"That... It can't... It can't be... You... Brought one of them back to... "
"life. I... I thought this was impossible... You can say I am... "
"flabbergasted. Well done, traveler. Expect... rewards before your next "
"journey.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1699
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ZOLTAN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[5]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1705
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ZOLTAN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[6]/text"
msgstr "Present your Revenant crew."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1707
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ZOLTAN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[6]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Is... is that an actual... ghost? I must say, I... didn't think it was "
"possible... to bring back the dead. Frankly... I can scarcely... believe my "
"own eyes... You can say I am... very... very... impressed. Well done, "
"traveler. Expect... rewards before your next journey.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1711
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ZOLTAN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[6]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1717
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ZOLTAN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[7]/text"
msgstr "Present your Snowman crew."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1719
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ZOLTAN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[7]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"A... living Snowman... It seems all those... stories for kids can... "
"actually happen... you learn... something new everyday... You can say I "
"am... very... impressed. Well done, traveler. Expect... rewards before your "
"next journey.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1723
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ZOLTAN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[7]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1729
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ZOLTAN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[8]/text"
msgstr "Present your Lavaman crew."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1731
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ZOLTAN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[8]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"A... living lava being... I suppose... something like that... was "
"eventually... going to be attempted... You can say I am... very... "
"impressed. Well done, traveler. Expect... rewards before your next "
"journey.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1735
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ZOLTAN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[8]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1741
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ZOLTAN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[9]/text"
msgstr "Present your AI Avatar crew."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1743
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ZOLTAN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[9]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Now that's... fascinating... it has no physical... body, and yet... it can"
" still interact... with us. You can very much... say that I'm impressed. "
"Well done, traveler. Expect... rewards before your next journey.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1747
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ZOLTAN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[9]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1756
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ROCKMAN_REAL\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Present a Commonwealth item."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1758
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ROCKMAN_REAL\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"But that... That EQUIPMENT! Renegade, you don't have the SMALLEST idea of "
"what you have in your HANDS do you? This equipment it's... I THOUGHT all of "
"it was DESTROYED by our FOREFATHERS! But seeing it with my own EYES then "
"maybe, maybe we might be ABLE to... BAH! What am I SAYING, it doesn't MATTER"
" anymore! NEVERTHELESS, I shall BLESS you with the BLESSING OF IONIZATION. "
"But have PATIENCE. It is not for now, but for LATER!\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1762
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ROCKMAN_REAL\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1768
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ROCKMAN_REAL\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Present a Salt gun."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1770
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ROCKMAN_REAL\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"A SALT GUN? Do you take ME for a FOOL, RENEGADE? I will have you KNOW I'm "
"personally not a FAN of SEASONING! REGARDLESS, this is tribute, I suppose, "
"so I shall BLESS you with the BLESSING OF SALT. But have PATIENCE. It is not"
" for now, but for LATER!\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1774
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ROCKMAN_REAL\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1780
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ROCKMAN_REAL\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Present a Revenant gun."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1782
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ROCKMAN_REAL\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"WHAT in the GREAT ADMIRAL'S top shape ARSE is THIS?! I have never SEEN "
"anything like this! WHERE did you acquire this WEIRD gun, RENEGADE? It's... "
"IT'S WONDERFUL! I shall BLESS you with the BLESSING OF THE UNDEAD. But have "
"PATIENCE. It is not for now, but for LATER!\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1786
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ROCKMAN_REAL\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[3]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1792
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ROCKMAN_REAL\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[4]/text"
msgstr "Present a Prototype item."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1794
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ROCKMAN_REAL\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"THIS... WEAPON. It's... the most BEAUTIFUL thing I have EVER seen! The "
"MATERIAL, the EXECUTION! All that's missing is some FIELD TESTING! Thank "
"you, RENEGADE, for showing me this BEAUTIFUL piece of TECHNOLOGY! I shall "
"BLESS you with the BLESSING OF PROTOTYPES. But have PATIENCE. It is not for "
"now, but for LATER!\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1798
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ROCKMAN_REAL\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[4]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1807
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ENGI_REAL\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/text"
msgstr "Present Her Will."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1809
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ENGI_REAL\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"[ERROR]... How d-d-d-did ... T-T-That shouldn't even be p-p-possible! N-N-"
"No... I-I need to w-warn the others! B-But... Corby would never b-b-b-break "
"the creed! So I must -reward- you still... I will give you the Grant of "
"Touch! Grant of Touch! Save it - for the future, and n-n-never t-talk to us "
"again!\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1813
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ENGI_REAL\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1822
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_NORMAL\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/text"
msgstr "Your Withered seems to be eager to present themselves to Thest."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1824
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_NORMAL\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Thest pauses as he analyzes the crew. After a few minutes, the Judge smiles. \"Ah... so someone has finally... come to reclaim the prize.\" He pauses for a moment, thinking, before handing you the blueprints for a Lanius-like ship!\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\"Someone sought us... long ago with a... simple request... if anyone were to... present a Lanius of this type... then we should give them these blueprints. Don't bother asking... who that was, as I'm... not sure who that was either. Enjoy your... prize, Renegade.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1834
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_NORMAL\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/event/choice[@req=\"prof_judges_zoltan\"]/text"
msgstr "Present yourself to Thest, Judge of Diplomacy."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1838
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_NORMAL\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/event/choice[@req=\"prof_judges_engi\"]/text"
msgstr "Present yourself to Corby, Judge of Technology."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1842
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_NORMAL\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/event/choice[@req=\"prof_judges_rockman\"]/text"
msgstr "Present yourself to Wakeson, Judge of Warfare."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1846
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_NORMAL\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/event/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "Present yourself to none of them."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1848
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_NORMAL\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/event/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr "\"Very... well. I understand. Safe travels then, traveler...\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1857
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ORACLE_AGAIN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/text"
msgstr "Your Withered seems to be eager to present themselves to Thest."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1859
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ORACLE_AGAIN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Thest pauses as he analyzes the crew. After a few minutes, the Judge smiles. \"Ah... so someone has finally... come to reclaim the prize.\" He pauses for a moment, thinking, before handing you the blueprints for a Lanius-like ship!\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\"Someone sought us... long ago with a... simple request... if anyone were to... present a Lanius of this type... then we should give them these blueprints. Don't bother asking... who that was, as I'm... not sure who that was either. Enjoy your... prize, Renegade.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1869
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ORACLE_AGAIN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/event/choice[@req=\"prof_judges_zoltan\"]/text"
msgstr "Present yourself to Thest, Judge of Diplomacy."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1873
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ORACLE_AGAIN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/event/choice[@req=\"prof_judges_engi\"]/text"
msgstr "Present yourself to Corby, Judge of Technology."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1877
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ORACLE_AGAIN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/event/choice[@req=\"prof_judges_rockman\"]/text"
msgstr "Present yourself to Wakeson, Judge of Warfare."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1881
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ORACLE_AGAIN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/event/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "Present yourself to none of them."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1883
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ORACLE_AGAIN\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/event/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr "\"Very... well. I understand. Safe travels then, traveler...\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1892
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ORACLE_FIRST\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/text"
msgstr "Your Withered seems to be eager to present themselves to Thest."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1894
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ORACLE_FIRST\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Thest pauses as he analyzes the crew. After a few minutes, the Judge smiles. \"Ah... so someone has finally... come to reclaim the prize.\" He pauses for a moment, thinking, before handing you the blueprints for a Lanius-like ship!\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\"Someone sought us... long ago with a... simple request... if anyone were to... present a Lanius of this type... then we should give them these blueprints. Don't bother asking... who that was, as I'm... not sure who that was either. Enjoy your... prize, Renegade.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1904
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ORACLE_FIRST\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/event/choice[@req=\"prof_judges_zoltan\"]/text"
msgstr "Present yourself to Thest, Judge of Diplomacy."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1908
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ORACLE_FIRST\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/event/choice[@req=\"prof_judges_engi\"]/text"
msgstr "Present yourself to Corby, Judge of Technology."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1912
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ORACLE_FIRST\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/event/choice[@req=\"prof_judges_rockman\"]/text"
msgstr "Present yourself to Wakeson, Judge of Warfare."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1916
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ORACLE_FIRST\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/event/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "Present yourself to none of them."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1918
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"THE_JUDGES_ORACLE_FIRST\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/event/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr "\"Very... well. I understand. Safe travels then, traveler...\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1963
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SALT_BATTLESHIP_QUEST_START\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Upon arriving at the prison, you notice it's completely empty, save for a single Auto-ship blocking the entrance. The prison is completely encased by lead plates, preventing any scans of the inside from here.\n"
"\t\n"
"\t    \"An Auto-ship? Why would the Rebellion put an auto-cruiser of all things here?\" Obyn ponders out loud. The cruiser ignores all of your hails, and the warning message spewing forth from its comms is somewhat distorted."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1968
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SALT_BATTLESHIP_QUEST_START\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Let's teach this hunk of metal who's boss!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1970
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SALT_BATTLESHIP_QUEST_START\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The ship's drones whirl to life, defending their mothership. This is gonna "
"be tough."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1973
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SALT_BATTLESHIP_QUEST_START\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1979
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SALT_BATTLESHIP_QUEST_START\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Leave the Auto-ship alone."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1981
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SALT_BATTLESHIP_QUEST_START\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You decide you have other more important things to do than chase a mystery. "
"Obyn is clearly unhappy, taking this moment to resign from your crew."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1984
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SALT_BATTLESHIP_QUEST_START\"]/choice[2]/event/removeCrew/text"
msgstr "Your crew cannot be cloned, as they are still alive."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1991
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SALT_BATTLESHIP_QUEST_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The giant Auto-ship breaks apart, finally silenced. After making sure its "
"systems are down, you park your ship next to the prison and go explore it "
"alongside Obyn."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1994
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SALT_BATTLESHIP_QUEST_WIN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:1996
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SALT_BATTLESHIP_QUEST_WIN\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The doors are unlocked - whoever built this facility likely thought the Auto-cruiser was enough defense. Within the facility, you find thousands upon thousands of pods, each holding... a number of whitish crystals. Salt people, once thought extinct, frozen in stasis!\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t  Obyn practically screams with elation. \"Captain! Holy shit... I... l-let me open 'em up!\" He sprints to a terminal on the side of the room, mashing away at the keyboard."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2000
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SALT_BATTLESHIP_QUEST_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2002
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SALT_BATTLESHIP_QUEST_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The grueling process of bringing the Salt people out of stasis slowly to avoid the risk of system shock takes multiple hours. Only one out of every ten pods ends up being viable for reanimation...but eventually, another Saltman dazedly steps out of their pod.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t  \"W-who...?\" the Salt person asks, looking around. \"It... it worked, Captain! It worked!\" Obyn jumps for joy, sitting down next to the newly refreshed Saltman. However, his joy briefly dampens as he pulls you aside. \"Captain... this may take days, or even weeks to sort out. You can't wait, but I can. I'm asking you... go on without me.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2010
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SALT_BATTLESHIP_QUEST_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Are you sure, Obyn?"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2012
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SALT_BATTLESHIP_QUEST_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Obyn looks over the many reunited families as they all step out of their pods. \"Yes, Captain. But there's no way I'm leaving you empty-handed.\" The formerly-sole surviving Saltman hands you a thumb drive. \"Here's the blueprints to a cruiser for my kin. I wanted to build it, but... I don't think that life is for me anymore. You'll get better use out of it.\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tHe steps forward, careful to not suck all the moisture out of you. \"Feel free to take the weapons from my ship. I won't be using them anymore, either...\" You nod, assuring him of his decision. One of the other Saltmen, inspired by your act of kindness, offers to join your crew. Although the Rebel fleet will certainly have caught up by now, you're not too mad about it."
